{"data":[{"date":"03:55 03/07","title":"4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n ng\u00e0y Neymar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng gi\u00fap Brazil h\u1ea1 Mexico 2-0","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/4-diem-nhan-ngay-neymar-toa-sang-giup-brazil-ha-mexico-20.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Brazil vs Mexico 2-0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu Neymar, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd kh\u00e1c, h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: </strong>Brazil 2-0 Mexico<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n:<br>\r\n- Brazil:</strong> Neymar 51', Firmino 88'<br>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video class=\"hlsvideoobj\" data-src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/HLS/201807/274880/master.m3u8\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>1. Mexico \u0111\u00e1nh bi\u00ean b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u, Mexico \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Brazil. Trong ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 Selecao v\u1eafng c\u1ea3 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh Marcelo v\u00e0 Danilo do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd xem \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch khai th\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Carlos Vela v\u00e0 Hirving Lozano li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Fagner v\u00e0 Filipe Luis. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Brazil \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Fagner c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n b\u1ed1i r\u1ed1i. 3 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mexico tung ra ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 20 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 n\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1edbi t\u1eeb hai bi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Brazil vs Mexico 2-0 Ng\u00e0y Neymar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Brazil vs Mexico 2-0 Ng\u00e0y Neymar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Diem-nhan-Brazil-vs-Mexico-2-0-Ngay-Neymar-toa-sang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mexico c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o hai c\u00e1nh Brazil</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn qua, k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Mexico \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 su\u1ed1t v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd: d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1ea1i xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n. T\u00ednh ra, El Tri \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 10 c\u00fa ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ec9 sau 20 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u bao g\u1ed3m 3 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3, Brazil nh\u1eadn ra \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Mexico v\u00e0 b\u1ecbt ch\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng l\u1ed7 h\u1ed5ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc M\u1ef9 kh\u00f4ng khi n\u00e0o c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ee9c \u00e9p l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-ruc-lua-tren-san-cosmos-ngay-brazil-loai-mexico-465-190227.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/nhung-hinh-anh-ruc-lua-tren-san-cosmos-ngay-brazil-loai-mexico.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-ruc-lua-tren-san-cosmos-ngay-brazil-loai-mexico-465-190227.html\">Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh r\u1ef1c l\u1eeda tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Cosmos ng\u00e0y Brazil lo\u1ea1i Mexico</span><br>\r\n<span>C\u00e1c kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i s\u00e2n Cosmos nh\u01b0 ch\u00e1y r\u1ef1c l\u00ean v\u1edbi n\u00e9t b\u1ed1c l\u1eeda t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p Nam M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean hai \u0111\u1ed9i trong ng\u00e0y Brazil \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n2. Brazil g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 khi thi\u1ebfu Marcelo</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, vi\u1ec7c tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Brazil \u1edf hai c\u00e1nh c\u0169ng k\u00e9m s\u1eafc n\u00e9t khi thi\u1ebfu Marcelo v\u00e0 Danilo, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Mexico gia t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u, HLV Tite ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb 4-3-3, Brazil chuy\u1ec3n sang 4-4-2 v\u1edbi Willian v\u00e0 Coutinho h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Marcelo trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, Neymar v\u00e0 Coutinho \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i v\u1eadt l\u1ed9n b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. Kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t xa nhau v\u00e0 tam gi\u00e1c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o d\u1ef1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t Filipe thi\u00ean qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Brazil vs Mexico Coutinho kho khan\" title=\"Brazil vs Mexico Coutinho kho khan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Brazil-vs-Mexico-Coutinho-kho-khan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Coutinho thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0103n \u00fd b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNeymar nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fac b\u1ecb c\u00f4 l\u1eadp \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u00ean v\u00e0 l\u00e2m v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng ph\u1ea3i &ldquo;t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m, t\u1ef1 \u0103n&rdquo;. Lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Mexico theo k\u00e8m s\u1ed1 10 v\u00e0 ngay c\u1ea3 khi anh v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua, h\u1ecd l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac Brazil ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 n\u0103m 2014, n\u01a1i h\u1ecd b\u1ecb Mexico c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 0-0 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>3. Neymar t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i d\u00e0nh cho Brazil v\u00e0 Neymar, nh\u01b0ng b\u00e0n khai th\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ee9u r\u1ed7i h\u1ecd. T\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0103ng ngang d\u1ecdn c\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Willian, Neymar c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1ed1ng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Selecao \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Mexico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar mo ty so cho Brazil\" title=\"Neymar mo ty so cho Brazil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Neymar-mo-ty-so-cho-Brazil.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Neymar l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Brazil vs Mexico</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng t\u1eeb b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, th\u1ebf c\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e3 xoay v\u1ea7n. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f4ng lao c\u1ee7a Neymar l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf. Anh thu h\u00fat t\u1edbi 5 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Mexico, m\u1edf ra kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng cho Willian b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u1ebbn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi ph\u00fat 88, c\u0169ng l\u1ea1i Neymar b\u1ee9t \u0111i r\u1ea5t nhanh, r\u1ea5t d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i v\u00e0 d\u00f9 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Mexico, v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh n\u00f3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n ngon \u0103n cho Roberto Firmino d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 cho Brazil. \u0110\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Brazil vs Mexico kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu Neymar.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/toa-sang-ruc-ro-truoc-mexico-nguoi-hung-neymar-noi-gi-421-190224.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/toa-sang-ruc-ro-truoc-mexico-nguoi-hung-neymar-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/toa-sang-ruc-ro-truoc-mexico-nguoi-hung-neymar-noi-gi-421-190224.html\">T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Neymar n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\n<span>Neymar ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Mexico, ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi Selecao v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, anh c\u0169ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n4. Brazil c\u1ea7n ch\u1ea5n ch\u1ec9nh l\u1ea1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBrazil \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 khi\u1ebfn HLV ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129. Paulinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebfu hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Anh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u trong thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ea7u n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Neymar, Jesus \u1edf tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBrazil kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd ch\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. V\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t l\u00ean b\u00f3ng nhanh t\u1eeb Mexico v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft d\u00ednh h\u01a1n tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Tite c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eaft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"casemiro tha vang truoc Brazil\" title=\"casemiro tha vang truoc Brazil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/casemiro-tha-vang-truoc-Brazil.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Casemiro s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi B\u1ec9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 2 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn, Casemiro s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, n\u01a1i Brazil \u0111\u1ee5ng B\u1ec9 (\u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi th\u1eafng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 3-2). Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, kh\u00e2u ch\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Selecao s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ec9 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhanh nh\u1eb9n, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Eden Hazard. S\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 d\u00e0nh cho Brazil v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1ee9 4 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. D\u00f9 sao, Selecao c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u<br>\r\nBrazil (4-3-3): </strong>Alisson; Fagner, T Silva, Miranda, Luis; Coutinho (Firmino 86'), Casemiro, Paulinho (Fernandinho 81') ; Neymar, Jesus, Willian (Marquinhos 91')<br>\r\n<strong>Mexico (4-3-3):</strong> Ochoa; Alvarez (Dos Santos 55'), Ayela, Salcedo, Gallardo; Herrera, Marquez (Layun 46'), Guardado; Vela, Hernandez (Kiminez 60'), Lozano<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Mexico tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/ha-guc-mexico-brazil-pha-ky-luc-cua-duc-tai-world-cup-465-190223.html\">H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Mexico, Brazil ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/willian-duoc-khen-ngoi-dac-biet-sau-chien-thang-cua-dt-brazil-465-190225.html\">Willian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen ng\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-osorio-chi-ra-khac-biet-khien-mexico-thua-brazil-465-190222.html\">HLV Osorio ch\u1ec9 ra kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t khi\u1ebfn Mexico thua Brazil</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-brazil-vs-mexico-463-190202.html\">Brazil 2-0 Mexico: Neymar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Selecao bay th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"831","checkdouble":"190231"},{"date":"03:29 03/07","title":"M\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t danh th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1c khi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n su\u00fdt l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/cac-cuu-danh-thu-len-tieng-khi-bi-thang-kich-tinh-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c danh th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 k\u00ecm n\u1ed5i li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh gi\u1eefa B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i World Cup 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ec9 th\u1eafng h\u00fa v\u00eda<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01a1i l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0110T B\u1ec9 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1ecb d\u1ed9i g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p hai. Haraguchi v\u00e0 Takashi Inui li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-0 khi hi\u1ec7p hai m\u1edbi qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6 ph\u00fat.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00e1c c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khi B\u1ec9 th\u1eafng k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00e1c c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khi B\u1ec9 th\u1eafng k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/cac-cuu-danh-thu-len-tieng-khi-bi-thang-kich-tinh-nhat-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u00e1c c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khi B\u1ec9 th\u1eafng k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u00f9 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc hai b\u00e0n.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh \u1edf l\u00fac c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. Vertonghen s\u1eeda sai v\u1edbi pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u r\u00fat ng\u1eafn c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t r\u1ed3i Fellaini g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a c\u0169ng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t pha kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn. \u0110\u00fang ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh, Chadli ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2 cho \u0110T B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c danh th\u1ee7 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng&quot; - Lucas Leiva \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i tr\u00ean Twitter k\u00e8m bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00e0ng v\u1ed7 tay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;World Cup wow! B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n m\u00e0 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn&quot; - Sol Campbell ti\u1ebfc cho nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a &quot;samurai xanh&quot;.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 k\u1ef3 World Cup tuy\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5t t\u00f4i t\u1eebng xem. N\u01b0\u1edbc Nga \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady \u0111\u00fang th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m. H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3&quot; - Gary Neville kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i s\u1ef1 h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng sau khi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n su\u00fdt l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xoay chuy\u1ec3n qu\u00e1 nhanh, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u01a1i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t. Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng B\u1ec9 khi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 cho \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Hoan h\u00f4&quot; - Patrick Kluivert \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt, B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Brazil \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 1h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-bi-vs-nhat-ban-421-190216.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-bi-vs-nhat-ban-463-190214.html\">B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n, B\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Brazil \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/eden-hazard-tu-tin-se-lam-tot-hon-messi-ronaldo-421-190195.html\">Eden Hazard t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Messi, Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/drogba-lukaku-se-giup-bi-lam-nen-chuyen-o-world-cup-2018-421-190171.html\">Drogba: Lukaku s\u1ebd gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n \u1edf World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-nhat-ban-muon-lam-nen-dia-chan-truoc-dt-bi-465-190159.html\">HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bi-vs-nhat-ban-1h00-ngay-37-lieu-co-them-dia-chan-462-190153.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (1h00 ng\u00e0y 3/7): Li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong> </strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"830","checkdouble":"190232"},{"date":"03:54 03/07","title":"HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd B\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng s\u1eafc b\u00e9n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/hlv-nhat-ban-tiec-vi-khong-thang-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Eden Hazard th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac B\u1ec9 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i khi b\u1ecb Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc hai b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y ch\u00f3ng v\u00e1nh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i World Cup 2018.</h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-nhat-ban-461-190228.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-nhat-ban.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-nhat-ban-461-190228.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 0-2 v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7p 2 ch\u1ec9 v\u1eeba m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, nh\u01b0ng B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ec9 t\u1eebng run s\u1ee3</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng \u0110T B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn. Sang hi\u1ec7p hai, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi hai l\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 6 ph\u00fat v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Haraguchi v\u00e0 Takashi Inui.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eden Hazard thua nhan Bi tung run so Nhat Ban khi bi dan truoc hai ban.\" title=\"Eden Hazard th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn B\u1ec9 t\u1eebng run s\u1ee3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc hai b\u00e0n.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/eden-hazard-thua-nhan-bi-tung-run-so-nhat-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Eden Hazard th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn B\u1ec9 t\u1eebng run s\u1ee3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc hai b\u00e0n.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u00f3, Eden Hazard th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn B\u1ec9 t\u1eebng run s\u1ee3: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 lo r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ed1ng hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi g\u1eb7p x\u1ee9 Wales t\u1ea1i Euro 2016. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u00ec v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. H\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Brazil<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen ng\u1ee3i v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u khi kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 d\u00f9 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Vertonghen \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa sai l\u1ea7m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1eb1ng c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u r\u00fat ng\u1eafn t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1, Fellaini g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a r\u1ed3i Chadli \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/eden-hazard-tu-tin-se-lam-tot-hon-messi-ronaldo-421-190195.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/eden-hazard-tu-tin-se-lam-tot-hon-messi-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/eden-hazard-tu-tin-se-lam-tot-hon-messi-ronaldo-421-190195.html\">Eden Hazard t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Messi, Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Eden Hazard t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap \u0110T B\u1ec9 t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brazil: &quot;Ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ki\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Khi nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u00e0ng c\u1ea3nh th\u1eadt r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brazil lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Brazil vs B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 1h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-nhat-ban-tiec-vi-khong-thang-bi-465-190233.html\">HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd B\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng s\u1eafc b\u00e9n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/cac-cuu-danh-thu-len-tieng-khi-bi-thang-kich-tinh-nhat-ban-465-190232.html\">M\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t danh th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1c khi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n su\u00fdt l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-bi-vs-nhat-ban-421-190216.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-bi-vs-nhat-ban-463-190214.html\">B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n, B\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Brazil \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-nhat-ban-muon-lam-nen-dia-chan-truoc-dt-bi-465-190159.html\">HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bi-vs-nhat-ban-1h00-ngay-37-lieu-co-them-dia-chan-462-190153.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (1h00 ng\u00e0y 3/7): Li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong> </strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"829","checkdouble":"190233"},{"date":"03:47 03/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Mexico","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-brazil-20-mexico.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Mexico v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Brazil \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf 8 trong s\u1ed1 9 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i World Cup tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c CONCACAF.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 n\u0103m 1986, Mexico \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a World Cup 7 l\u1ea7n, nhi\u1ec1u \u00edt nh\u1ea5t g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Brazil b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 15 tr\u1eadn t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua, ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Mexico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Mexico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Diem-nhan-Brazil-vs-Mexico-2-0-Ngay-Neymar-toa-sang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Fagner tranh b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi Vela \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Mexico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- Roberto Firmino ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Brazil 2-0 Mexico ch\u1ec9 2 ph\u00fat 4 gi\u00e2y sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, nhanh th\u1ee9 2 cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Firmino \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 7 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Brazil, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng pha \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Neymar \u0111\u00e3 tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o 20 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 19 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y cho Brazil, ghi 11 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o 9 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Neymar l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m (23), tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t (12) v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t (16) t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Neymar \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng World Cup t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay, b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Lionel Messi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- N\u1ebfu Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi c\u1ea7n 74 v\u00e0 67 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1edbi c\u00f3 6 b\u00e0n, Neymar ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 38 pha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Guillermo Ochoa c\u1ee7a Mexico \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 8 pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, ch\u1ec9 1 l\u1ea7n c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01a1n th\u1ebf t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, l\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Ochoa tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng (9).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Rafael Marquez (39 tu\u1ed5i 139 ng\u00e0y) tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng knock-out World Cup, sau Stanley Matthews (39 tu\u1ed5i 145 ng\u00e0y) n\u0103m 1954.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Mexico tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/toa-sang-ruc-ro-truoc-mexico-nguoi-hung-neymar-noi-gi-421-190224.html\">T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Neymar n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/ha-guc-mexico-brazil-pha-ky-luc-cua-duc-tai-world-cup-465-190223.html\">H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Mexico, Brazil ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-osorio-chi-ra-khac-biet-khien-mexico-thua-brazil-465-190222.html\">HLV Osorio ch\u1ec9 ra kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t khi\u1ebfn Mexico thua Brazil</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-brazil-vs-mexico-463-190202.html\">Brazil 2-0 Mexico: Neymar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Selecao bay th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"828","checkdouble":"190234"},{"date":"04:13 03/07","title":"Thua \u0111au Brazil, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Mexico ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Neymar gi\u1ecfi di\u1ec5n k\u1ecbch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/doi-truong-mexico-che-neymar-gioi-dien-kich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thua Brazil \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 7 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i World Cup 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Mexico ch\u00ea Neymar gi\u1ecfi \u0111\u00f3ng k\u1ecbch khi va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi Layun.</h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-mexico-461-190212.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/13.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-mexico-461-190212.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Brazil 2-0 Mexico (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao Neymar m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 r\u1ed3i ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Firmino ghi b\u00e0n, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mexico 2-0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Mexico ch\u00ea Neymar</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ghi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Firmino, Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Neymar \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i v\u1edbi Mexico sau pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi Layun. \u0110T Mexico cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00ean ph\u00eda Brazil c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh \u0103n v\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2u th\u1ebb.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Mexico ch\u00ea Neymar gi\u1ecfi di\u1ec5n k\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Mexico ch\u00ea Neymar gi\u1ecfi di\u1ec5n k\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/doi-truong-mexico-che-neymar-gioi-dien-kich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Mexico ch\u00ea Neymar gi\u1ecfi di\u1ec5n k\u1ecbch sau tr\u1eadn thua Brazil.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, Layun ra nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 d\u1eabm v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n Neymar. Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, Neymar qu\u1eb1n qu\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng sau khi h\u1ecfi tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd VAR, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Gianluca Rocchi kh\u00f4ng r\u00fat th\u1ebb v\u1edbi Layun.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Andres Guardado - \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Mexico ch\u00ea Neymar di\u1ec5n k\u1ecbch: &quot;Ai ch\u1ea3 bi\u1ebft Neymar nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. T\u00f4i hay ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1n x\u00e9t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0ng FIFA v\u00e0 VAR th\u00ec c\u00f3. Gi\u1edd ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 VAR, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem c\u00e1ch anh ta ch\u01a1i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i c\u1ea7n n\u00f3 b\u1edfi Neymar th\u00edch th\u1ed5i ph\u1ed3ng nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i, anh ta l\u0103n xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a anh ta, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u00e1n x\u00e9t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5m g\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ea5u Neymar<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Neymar, HLV Osorio cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 t\u1ea5m g\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ea5u: &quot;Th\u1eadt x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 khi m\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. M\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ed1n ph\u00fat ch\u1eadm tr\u1ec5 ch\u1ec9 cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u1ea5m g\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ea5u cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;\u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u g\u00e3 h\u1ec1 bu quanh&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thua tr\u1eadn, Mexico v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 7 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i World Cup. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Brazil s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n B\u1ec9 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0o 1h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil vs Mexico:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-brazil-20-mexico-421-190234.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Mexico</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-diem-nhan-ngay-neymar-toa-sang-giup-brazil-ha-mexico-20-421-190231.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n ng\u00e0y Neymar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng gi\u00fap Brazil h\u1ea1 Mexico 2-0</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-ruc-lua-tren-san-cosmos-ngay-brazil-loai-mexico-465-190227.html\">Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh r\u1ef1c l\u1eeda tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Cosmos ng\u00e0y Brazil lo\u1ea1i Mexico</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-tite-phat-bieu-ve-tran-brazil-vs-mexico-421-190226.html\">HLV Tite: Brazil c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i c\u00e0ng hay \u1edf World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/willian-duoc-khen-ngoi-dac-biet-sau-chien-thang-cua-dt-brazil-465-190225.html\">Willian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen ng\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/toa-sang-ruc-ro-truoc-mexico-nguoi-hung-neymar-noi-gi-421-190224.html\">T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Neymar n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong> </strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"827","checkdouble":"190235"},{"date":"04:28 03/07","title":"Eden Hazard th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn B\u1ec9 t\u1eebng run s\u1ee3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/eden-hazard-thua-nhan-bi-tung-run-so-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Eden Hazard th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac B\u1ec9 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i khi b\u1ecb Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc hai b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y ch\u00f3ng v\u00e1nh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i World Cup 2018.</h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-nhat-ban-461-190228.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-nhat-ban.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-nhat-ban-461-190228.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 0-2 v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7p 2 ch\u1ec9 v\u1eeba m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, nh\u01b0ng B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ec9 t\u1eebng run s\u1ee3</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng \u0110T B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn. Sang hi\u1ec7p hai, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi hai l\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 6 ph\u00fat v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Haraguchi v\u00e0 Takashi Inui.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eden Hazard thua nhan Bi tung run so Nhat Ban khi bi dan truoc hai ban.\" title=\"Eden Hazard th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn B\u1ec9 t\u1eebng run s\u1ee3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc hai b\u00e0n.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/eden-hazard-thua-nhan-bi-tung-run-so-nhat-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Eden Hazard th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn B\u1ec9 t\u1eebng run s\u1ee3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc hai b\u00e0n.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u00f3, Eden Hazard th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn B\u1ec9 t\u1eebng run s\u1ee3: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 lo r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ed1ng hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi g\u1eb7p x\u1ee9 Wales t\u1ea1i Euro 2016. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u00ec v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. H\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Brazil<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen ng\u1ee3i v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u khi kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 d\u00f9 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Vertonghen \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa sai l\u1ea7m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1eb1ng c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u r\u00fat ng\u1eafn t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1, Fellaini g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a r\u1ed3i Chadli \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/eden-hazard-tu-tin-se-lam-tot-hon-messi-ronaldo-421-190195.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/eden-hazard-tu-tin-se-lam-tot-hon-messi-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/eden-hazard-tu-tin-se-lam-tot-hon-messi-ronaldo-421-190195.html\">Eden Hazard t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Messi, Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Eden Hazard t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap \u0110T B\u1ec9 t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brazil: &quot;Ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ki\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Khi nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u00e0ng c\u1ea3nh th\u1eadt r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brazil lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Brazil vs B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 1h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-nhat-ban-tiec-vi-khong-thang-bi-465-190233.html\">HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd B\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng s\u1eafc b\u00e9n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/cac-cuu-danh-thu-len-tieng-khi-bi-thang-kich-tinh-nhat-ban-465-190232.html\">M\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t danh th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1c khi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n su\u00fdt l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-bi-vs-nhat-ban-421-190216.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-bi-vs-nhat-ban-463-190214.html\">B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n, B\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Brazil \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-nhat-ban-muon-lam-nen-dia-chan-truoc-dt-bi-465-190159.html\">HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bi-vs-nhat-ban-1h00-ngay-37-lieu-co-them-dia-chan-462-190153.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (1h00 ng\u00e0y 3/7): Li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong> </strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"826","checkdouble":"190236"},{"date":"04:48 03/07","title":"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-tran-bi-32-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc 0-2 nh\u01b0ng B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 3-2 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>1966 \u2013</strong> T\u1eeb n\u0103m 1966 \u0111\u1ebfn nay (B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 0-3 sau \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i 5-3) m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau khi thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n trong 90 ph\u00fat \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n - V\u00f2ng 18 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n - V\u00f2ng 18 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Thong-ke-Bi-vs-Nhat-Ban---Vong-18-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u1ec9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft sau cu\u1ed9c l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>1 -</strong> B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Genki Haraguchi l\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>10 - </strong>B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 10 thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u0103m 2006 (11).</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>1 \u2013</strong> Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadn B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean 2 l\u1ea7n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>6 \u2013</strong> Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf World Cup 2018, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 h\u1ecd ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n4 \u2013 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00e1ch nhau 4 ph\u00fat 16 gi\u00e2y c\u00f2n 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 c\u00e1ch nhau 4 ph\u00fat 30 gi\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>90 \u2013</strong> B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 3-2 c\u1ee7a Chadli v\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9 90 \u1edf World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chadli ghi ban an dinh chien thang cho DT Bi.\" title=\"Chadli ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0110T B\u1ec9.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/030818-chadli.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chadli ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0110T B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>19 -</strong> Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tham gia 19 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 18 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T B\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Roberto Martinez (10 b\u00e0n, 9 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>3 - </strong>Takashi Inui l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 ba ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n 1 th\u1eafng trong m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup cho Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, sau Junichi Inamoto n\u0103m 2002 (2) v\u00e0 Keisuke Honda v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2010 (2).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>2 \u2013 </strong>C\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Fellaini cho B\u1ec9 \u1edf World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>11 \u2013</strong> V\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Nacer Chadli \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t chu\u1ed7i 11 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n cho \u0110T B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"825","checkdouble":"190237"},{"date":"05:06 03/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, HLV B\u1ec9 n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/050328-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Roberto Martinez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, c\u1ef1u HLV Everton \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ec9 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 0-0 trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed 10 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2 B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ghi 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Roberto Martinez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Roberto Martinez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/HLV-Roberto-Martinez-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Bi-vs-Nhat-Ban-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T B\u1ec9 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 3-2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 5 ph\u00fat, t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 59 \u0111\u1ebfn 64, Jan Vertonghen v\u00e0 Fellaini \u0111\u00e3 ghi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chadli \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 3-2. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-bi-vs-nhat-ban-421-190216.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n </span>gi\u00fap Eden Hazard v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Brazil, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea9ng cao \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Roberto Martinez \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Roberto Martinez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, c\u1ef1u HLV Everton \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roberto Martinez danh gia cao tinh than cua Bi\" title=\"Roberto Martinez \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/050328-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Roberto Martinez \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o, h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-nguoc-dong-kho-tin-cua-bi-truoc-nhat-ban-421-190239.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-nguoc-dong-kho-tin-cua-bi-truoc-nhat-ban.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-nguoc-dong-kho-tin-cua-bi-truoc-nhat-ban-421-190239.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00f3 tin c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u00f9 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 2-0 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-3 qua \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. C\u00f9ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1ea5n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cH\u00f4m nay l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 h\u1ecd. B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00f3 tin nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"824","checkdouble":"190238"},{"date":"04:27 03/07","title":"4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00f3 tin c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-nguoc-dong-kho-tin-cua-bi-truoc-nhat-ban.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u00f9 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 2-0 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-3 qua \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. C\u00f9ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Romelu Lukaku</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRomelu Lukaku l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n - V\u00f2ng 18 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n - V\u00f2ng 18 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/4-diem-nhan-Bi-vs-Nhat-Ban---Vong-18-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lukaku b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Lukaku b\u1ecb c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n chia c\u1eaft ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh nh\u01b0 Eden Hazard hay Kevin de Bruyne, gi\u1eefa b\u1ed9 ba n\u00e0y g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p n\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 Maya Yoshida \u0111\u00e3 theo k\u00e8m r\u1ea5t s\u00e1t Lukaku khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ra h\u1ed3n trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Sang hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 khi B\u1ec9 d\u1ed3n \u00e9p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Lukaku c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00fat 61, Meunier t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 Lukaku b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ai k\u00e8m v\u00e0 \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng anh l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng ra ngo\u00e0i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1edbi ph\u00fat 86, Chadli t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 Lukaku b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00eanh m\u00f4ng song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 l\u1ea1i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kawashima \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ed1ng k\u00ea B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 6 l\u1ea7n (nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n), nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n n\u00e0o.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Jan Vertonghen t\u1eeb t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7p 2 di\u1ec5n ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 ph\u00fat, trung v\u1ec7 Jan Vertonghen m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng khi\u1ebfn B\u1ec9 nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua. T\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Shibasaki, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Tottenham \u0111\u1ee1 h\u1ee5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 Haraguchi b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Courtois trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vertonghen sua sai voi ban thang rut ngan cach biet cho DT Bi.\" title=\"Vertonghen s\u1eeda sai v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng r\u00fat ng\u1eafn c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t cho \u0110T B\u1ec9.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/vertonghen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Vertonghen s\u1eeda sai v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng r\u00fat ng\u1eafn c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t cho \u0110T B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Jan Vertonghen sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng chu\u1ed9c t\u1ed9i. Ph\u00fat 69, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n sai t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0nh b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c nh\u00ecn b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00e0n r\u00fat ng\u1eafn t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 1-2 c\u1ee7a Vertonghen ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1edfi B\u1ec9 sau khi c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i th\u0103ng hoa v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 3-2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVertonghen \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ebfm tr\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c gi\u1eefa t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00e0i t\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a HLV Roberto Martinez</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c v\u1edbi Anh \u1edf b\u1ea3ng G \u0111\u1ec1u quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3n s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Kompany.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fellaini danh dau go hoa 2-2\" title=\"Fellaini \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/024633-fellaini.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fellaini v\u00e0 Chadli v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u ghi b\u00e0n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t sung s\u1ee9c nh\u01b0ng B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u1ecd b\u1ebf t\u1eafc to\u00e0n t\u1eadp khi kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn B\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 2 b\u00e0n thua ch\u1ec9 trong 10 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2. Trong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u00f3 HLV Roberto Martinez \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Mertens v\u00e0 Carrasco r\u1eddi s\u00e2n nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Chadli v\u00e0 Fellaini.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ef1u HLV Everton t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng. Fellaini l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 sau qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard.&nbsp;\u0110\u00fang v\u00e0o ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Chadli ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1ea7m v\u00e0ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0ng r\u01a1i</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt r\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p l\u00fd trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi B\u1ec9. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u khi\u1ebfn B\u1ec9 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, sau \u0111\u00f3 lui v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Takashi Inui ghi ban thang nang ti so len 2-0 cho DT Nhat Ban.\" title=\"Takashi Inui ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e2ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0 cho \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/022207-inui.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-0 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 chia c\u1eaft nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady h\u1ecd c\u00f2n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb ph\u00fat 48 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 52, Genki Haraguchi v\u00e0 Takashi Inui ghi li\u1ec1n 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf hoa Anh \u0111\u00e0o v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-0.&nbsp;Tuy&nbsp;nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Eiji Kawashima m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i trong b\u00e0n r\u00fat ng\u1eafn t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 1-2 c\u1ee7a Vertonghen \u1edf ph\u00fat 69, ch\u1ec9 sau \u0111\u00f3 5 ph\u00fat kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng k\u00e9m khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1ec3 Fellaini g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ed3n l\u00ean t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 th\u00eam gi\u1edd. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00ednh tham v\u1ecdng k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u trong 90 ph\u00fat khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh, Meunier c\u0103ng ngang thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 Chadli \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2 cho B\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. <span href=\"http://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-bi-vs-nhat-ban-421-190216.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span> \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Martinez \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Brazil \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-0 nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i 3-2, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft tr\u00e1ch m\u00ecnh. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1966 \u0111\u1ebfn nay m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n trong 90 ph\u00fat \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"823","checkdouble":"190239"},{"date":"06:54 03/07","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil 2-0 Mexico: Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Neymar kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/3/du-am-brazil-20-mexico-gia-tri-cua-neymar-khong-chi-o-nhung-ban-thang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Neymar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o gi\u00fap Brazil \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mexico v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0 qua \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 10 trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng hay c\u00e1c pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Neymar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, Brazil c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico. Selecao ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0. Tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Mexico ch\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 samba l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil 2-0 Mexico Neymar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil 2-0 Mexico Neymar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Du-am-Brazil-2-0-Mexico-Neymar-toa-sang-khong-chi-o-ban-thang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neymar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNeymar \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico. Ph\u00fat 51, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m Mexico, anh gi\u1eadt g\u00f3t \u0111\u1ec3 Willian c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0103ng ngang \u0111\u00fang t\u1ea7m b\u0103ng v\u00e0o c\u1ee7a Neymar, trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ai k\u00e8m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Brazil cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u00f3a b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nOchoa, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f3 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ee9u thua l\u00ean t\u1edbi 81% \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Neymar.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 227 c\u1ee7a Brazil \u1edf World Cup, \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0110\u1ee9c trong danh s\u00e1ch c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t, trong khi &ldquo;ti\u1ec3u Pele&rdquo; c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 6 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i, b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Roberto Rivelino v\u00e0 Bebeto.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar noi ve tran Brazil vs Mexico\" title=\"Neymar n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/toa-sang-ruc-ro-truoc-mexico-nguoi-hung-neymar-noi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neymar x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen ng\u1ee3i sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNeymar \u0111\u00e3 ghi 6 b\u00e0n \u1edf World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 sau 38 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Cristiano Ronaldo (74) v\u00e0 Lionel Messi (67).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Brazil \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup, \u0111i\u1ec1u Messi hay Ronaldo d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc qua tu\u1ed5i 30 nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3&nbsp;l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Mexico l\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9 57 sau 89 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Brazil c\u1ee7a Neymar.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 88, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi Ochoa v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o trong, m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Mexico rung l\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ebft th\u00fac ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Neymar l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0o thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Roberto Firmino, th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 \u00edt, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Mexico l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Neymar \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Mexico l\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Anh d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 7 l\u1ea7n, 4 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ngo\u00e0i ra s\u1ed1 10 c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o ra 5 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, Neymar ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 c\u1ee7a Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Neymar</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Neymar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o gi\u00fap Brazil \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mexico v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0 qua \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 10 trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng hay c\u00e1c pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar chua co mot co hoi ro rang nao\" title=\"Neymar ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng n\u00e0o\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Ket-qua-Brazil-vs-Mexico-ket-qua-bong-da-vong-18-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neymar tham gia nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Brazil</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, Neymar \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tham gia v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 di chuy\u1ec3n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. &ldquo;Ti\u1ec3u Pele&rdquo; th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ch\u01a1i xa khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 nhi\u1ec7t cho th\u1ea5y anh ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNeymar ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5p trong vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft, \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-brazil-20-mexico-421-190234.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Brazil vs Mexico</span> cho th\u1ea5y trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Neymar l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Brazil, x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n (sau Casemiro).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNeymar \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u01b0 duy ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. Thay v\u00ec ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cung c\u1ea5p c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 kh\u1edfi x\u01b0\u1edbng cho nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThay v\u00ec nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng x\u1eed l\u00fd m\u00e0u m\u00e8 th\u00ec anh ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, Neymar c\u0169ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Mexico anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Coutinho, Jesus v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Willian.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ban do nhiet cua Neymar o tran dau voi Mexico\" title=\"B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Neymar \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/neymar-7.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Neymar \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Mexico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Brazil th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u1eadt nh\u1ea3 v\u1edbi Willian sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Neymar \u0111\u1ebfn theo k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Neymar l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 (23 l\u1ea7n), tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t (12), t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i (16) v\u00e0 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t (23).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Neymar v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Brazil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh x\u1ea5u x\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNeymar s\u1ebd c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ean anh sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u00e2u gi\u1edd, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch nh\u1eafm v\u00e0o s\u1ed1 10, h\u1ecd cho r\u1eb1ng anh \u0103n v\u1ea1 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch th\u00f4 thi\u1ec3n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Neymar c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 b\u1edfi anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Brazil \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"822","checkdouble":"190245"},{"date":"16:58 02/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn M.U chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/8/nguoi-nha-xac-nhan-mu-chuan-bi-co-tan-binh-thu-3.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh gia Craig Norwood, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lee Grant chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nM.U s\u1eafp c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tranh th\u1ee7 th\u1eddi gian c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tham d\u1ef1 World Cup, Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 BL\u0110 Man United \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm ch\u1ed1t t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng bom t\u1ea5n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd \u0111em v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Lee Grant \u2013 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 do, sau khi h\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Stoke.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m nay 35 tu\u1ed5i, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh sinh ra t\u1ea1i Anh n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 3 t\u1ea1i Old Trafford \u2013 sau David De Gea v\u00e0 Sergio Romero. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n cho r\u1eb1ng Grant s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf De Gea ra \u0111i c\u0169ng s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf, khi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh T\u00e2y Ban Nha chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a, M.U s\u1ebd g\u1eedi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Joel Pereira cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 21 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh cho m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh mu\u1ed1n CLB cho m\u00ecnh \u0111i \u201cdu h\u1ecdc\u201d. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, M.U c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, n\u00ean h\u1ecd s\u1ebd th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o g\u1eedi anh sang \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lee Grant h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lee Grant h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Nguoi-nha-xac-nhan-MU-chieu-mo-Lee-Grant-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lee Grant chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>\u00a0</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh gia Craig Norwood, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a CLB \u2013 \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh Lee Grant trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o m\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Norwood \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 2 t\u00e2n binh Fred v\u00e0 Diogo Dalot \u2013 ch\u1ec9 1 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi CLB \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao 1m93 v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m chinh chi\u1ebfn \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 35 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho Man United. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3i qua l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau, v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Romero \u0111\u1ebfn nay v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lee Grant, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/mot-doi-bong-tu-choi-co-hoi-chieu-mo-pogba-serbia-176-190157.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/16/mot-doi-bong-tu-choi-co-hoi-chieu-mo-pogba-serbia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/mot-doi-bong-tu-choi-co-hoi-chieu-mo-pogba-serbia-176-190157.html\">M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pogba Serbia</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e1n ng\u1ea5y v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb Lazio.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ben-do-moi-cua-martial-neu-roi-mu-172-190097.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/day-ben-do-moi-cua-martial-neu-roi-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ben-do-moi-cua-martial-neu-roi-mu-172-190097.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! B\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Martial n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi MU?</span><br>\r\nBayern Munich mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p r\u1eddi Old Trafford nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u00f4i sao...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-gay-soc-vu-muc-tieu-hang-dau-cua-liverpool-172-190006.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/mu-muon-gay-soc-vu-muc-tieu-hang-dau-cua-liverpool.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-gay-soc-vu-muc-tieu-hang-dau-cua-liverpool-172-190006.html\">MU mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span><br>\r\nMU mu\u1ed1n mua Nabil Fekir, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. \u0110\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t The Kop, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi \u0111\u1ee7 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"821","checkdouble":"190176"},{"date":"16:13 02/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng cho c\u1ea7u \u0111inh Brazil vs Mexico","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-mexico-va-du-doan-soi-keo-mexico-vs-brazil.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Mexico kh\u00f4ng ai ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n. Phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn d\u00f9 theo nh\u1eefng phong c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c nhau.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (\u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Brazil th\u1eafng 2-1<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: Brazil vs Mexico<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi gian: 21h ng\u00e0y 2/7<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: S\u00e2n Samara Arena<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: Brazil 0.87*0:1*-0.92 Mexico<br>\r\nTBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: Nhi\u1ec1u 0.96*2 1/2*0.97 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Mexico v\u00e0 d\u01b0 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Mexico v\u00e0 d\u01b0 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-mexico-va-du-doan-soi-keo-mexico-vs-brazil.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Mexico 21h ng\u00e0y 2/7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi Brazil, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. L\u00fd do HLV Dunga b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00edch m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u1edf c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. Tite l\u00ean nh\u1eadm ch\u1ee9c thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 r\u00fat ra kinh nghi\u1ec7m s\u00e2u s\u1eafc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2u, Tite c\u0169ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap Brazil ghi th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi nay, sau 24 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Selecao, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh 19 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng (t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 79,17%), ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi 52 b\u00e0n (trung b\u00ecnh 2,1 b\u00e0n/ tr\u1eadn).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Brazil nhe nhang vuot qua Serbia\" title=\"Brazil nhe nhang vuot qua Serbia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/thay-gi-trong-ngay-brazil-nhe-nhang-ha-serbia-20.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Brazil c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBrazil kh\u00f4ng khi n\u00e0o thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao v\u00e0 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng v\u1eady. T\u1eeb Neymar, Coutinho t\u1edbi Jesus, Willian r\u1ed3i Douglas Costa, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn trong nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. 7 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 giao h\u1eefu, c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 5 l\u00e0 h\u1ecd ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Brazil l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Mexico kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ph\u00eda. Mexico s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 m\u0169 r\u1ed9ng v\u00e0nh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1eed th\u1ee7 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/giai-ma-mexico-tai-world-cup-2018-qua-nhanh-qua-nguy-hiem-466-189773.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/giai-ma-mexico-tai-world-cup-2018-qua-nhanh-qua-nguy-hiem.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/giai-ma-mexico-tai-world-cup-2018-qua-nhanh-qua-nguy-hiem-466-189773.html\">Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 Mexico t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: Qu\u00e1 nhanh, qu\u00e1 nguy hi\u1ec3m</span><br>\r\n<span>T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Mexico c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i r\u00ecnh r\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7y nguy...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e3y nh\u00ecn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Mexico tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c. 42% th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00f3ng l\u0103n l\u00e0 b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Mexico nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 b\u00ean c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c. C\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n c\u1ee7a Mexico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Osorio tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng s\u00f2ng ph\u1eb3ng c\u00f9ng \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 sau c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u00fang l\u1eddi h\u1ee9a. Mexico l\u00f9i s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0ng lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 3 m\u0169i c\u00f4ng \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u00ean bao g\u1ed3m Hirving Lozano, Carlos Vela v\u00e0 Chicharito.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Mexico tai World Cup 2018 dang co nhung don tan cong chop nhoang ma ban thang cua Lozano la vi du dien hinh.\" title=\"\u0110T Mexico t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1edbp nho\u00e1ng m\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Lozano l\u00e0 v\u00ed d\u1ee5 \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/mexico-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mexico ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 khoa h\u1ecdc</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tho\u00e1t pressing c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, Mexico lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi ch\u00e2n c\u00e1c m\u0169i c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng El Tri c\u00f3 2, 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean ti\u1ec1n tuy\u1ebfn \u00e1p s\u00e1t c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c. N\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ch\u1eaft chiu h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd sau c\u00f9ng, s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n con s\u1ed1 1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n tr\u00ean s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mexico t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil. Hai c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i t\u1ed1t l\u00e0nh cho El Tri khai th\u00e1c. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/da-co-ket-luan-ve-kha-nang-da-chinh-cua-marcelo-truoc-mexico-421-190145.html\" target=\"_blank\">Marcelo ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span> trong khi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Danilo c\u00f2n l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marcelo roi san som do chan thuong\" title=\"Marcelo roi san som do chan thuong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Truoc-tran-gap-Mexico,-HLV-Tite-phat-bieu-ve-Marcelo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Marcelo v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, Filipe Luis v\u00e0 Fagner s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn 2 c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Brazil. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb, nh\u01b0ng thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 2. \u0110\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng r\u1ee7i ro x\u1ea3y ra, Brazil bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea5y c\u00f4ng b\u00f9 th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Mexico kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1edfi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng Brazil v\u1edbi h\u1ecfa l\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu b\u00f3 tay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBrazil s\u1ebd nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 c\u1ee7a Mexico tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc cho m\u00ecnh. Nh\u1eefng pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n, nhanh ch\u00f3ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng 5 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Link xem truc tiep Brazil vs Mexico\" title=\"Link xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Brazil vs Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/link-xem-brazil-vs-mexico.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">90 ph\u00fat tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Samara Arena s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Tite c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 khoan ph\u00e1 \u201cb\u00ea t\u00f4ng\u201d. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u01b0\u1eddi, Brazil c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb xa c\u1ee7a Willian, Coutinho. C\u0169ng ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi Neymar s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ed3i v\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn, Brazil \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Paulinho r\u1ed3i c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 Miranda, Thiago Silva s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tham chi\u1ebfn. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean s\u1eb5n \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong t\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00e1c nhau. M\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u201cqu\u00e2n b\u00e0i trong tay \u00e1o\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil vs Mexico h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. M\u1ed1c 2,5 b\u00e0n m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng m\u00e0 gi\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1eb7t ra \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Samara Arena t\u1ed1i nay, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (\u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Brazil th\u1eafng 2-1<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- T\u1ed5ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u1ebb<br>\r\n- Mexico kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 10 (O 9 1/2)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 5 (O 4 1/2)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 4 (O 4)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Brazil nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 (-2 1/2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a Brazil nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 (-1 1/4)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ly (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"820","checkdouble":"190178"},{"date":"16:56 02/07","title":"Salah gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p t\u1eeb Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/hlv-klopp-phat-bieu-ve-viec-salah-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Jeremie Aliadiere kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Pogba v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 v\u00ec Mourinho.</h2><h2>Pogba ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man United \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng khi \u0111\u01b0a Pogba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford h\u00e8 2016. Sau 4 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Juventus, Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0m m\u01b0a l\u00e0m gi\u00f3 t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e2y gi\u1edd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/pogba-len-tieng-dap-tra-nhung-chi-trich-172-187755.html\" target=\"_blank\">ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</span>. Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Mournho v\u00e0 c\u0169ng nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho \u0111ang k\u00ecm h\u00e3m Pogba \u1edf MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho \u0111ang k\u00ecm h\u00e3m Pogba \u1edf MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Mourinho-dang-kim-ham-Pogba-o-MU-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Aliadiere cho r\u1eb1ng Mourinho \u0111ang k\u00ecm h\u00e3m Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Aliadiere \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Pogba trong th\u1eddi gian qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cTh\u1eadt kh\u00f3 cho Pogba khi HLV kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n. V\u00e0 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 n\u0103m tr\u1eddi. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1i ki\u1ec3u \u2018t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a \u1edf Man United nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 cho Ph\u00e1p\u2019.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i nh\u1edb khi Pogba \u1edf Juventus, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gia nh\u1eadp Man United, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c Mourinho kh\u00f4ng trao cho Pogba nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao h\u01a1n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 duy tr\u00ec vi\u1ec7c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pogba m\u1ea5t gi\u00e1 \u1edf tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a Pogba trong l\u00f2ng NHM Man United c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ee5t gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. S\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn, Pogba mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1ea1i t\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec\u201d, Aliadiere n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn 100% s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina nh\u1edd t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i xung quanh ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng khi ch\u00fang ta th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n Pogba, c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean nhanh ch\u00f3ng th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u1edf \u0111\u00f3 n\u1eefa\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Pogba:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/pogba-tang-boc-mbappe-len-may-sau-tran-dai-thang-argentina-469-190086.html\">Pogba th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng b\u1eb1ng Mbappe</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/pogba-phan-phao-truoc-nhung-chi-trich-cua-cdv-phap-469-189872.html\">Pogba ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a C\u0110V Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"819","checkdouble":"190179"},{"date":"16:55 02/07","title":"Danny Welbeck ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/danny-welbeck-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-lam-ban-cua-dt-anh-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Danny Welbeck mu\u1ed1n \u0110T Anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Colombia t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup, \u0110T Anh n\u1eb1m trong nh\u00f3m 3 \u0111\u1ed9i ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t (8), b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi Nga v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m B\u1ec9 (9). \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 Tam S\u01b0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 6 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng &quot;b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danny Welbeck muon DT Anh tan dung bong chet tai World Cup 2018.\" title=\"Danny Welbeck mu\u1ed1n \u0110T Anh t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/danny-welbeck-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-lam-ban-cua-dt-anh-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Danny Welbeck mu\u1ed1n \u0110T Anh t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o nguy hi\u1ec3m cho Colombia khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, c\u1ea3 hai b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a Colombia \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n khi b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eeb s\u1edbm, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng pha &quot;b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft&quot;.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Welbeck mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Colombia, Danny Welbeck mu\u1ed1n \u0110T Anh t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m b\u00e0n: &quot;V\u1edbi c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o ra th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. C\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nguy hi\u1ec3m. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n t\u1eeb b\u00f3ng s\u1ed1ng&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Danny Welbeck c\u0169ng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1eb1ng Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Colombia: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u00e2n t\u00edch th\u1eadt k\u1ef9. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 y\u1ebfu n\u00ean s\u1ebd d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 khai th\u00e1c. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Colombia vs Anh s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 1h00 ng\u00e0y 4/7.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-arsenal-len-tieng-de-doa-dt-anh-421-190170.html\">Sao Arsenal l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0110T Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dele-alli-noi-cung-truoc-tran-gap-colombia-421-190166.html\">Dele Alli n\u00f3i c\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Colombia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lingard-phat-bieu-ve-dt-anh-tai-world-cup-2018-421-190149.html\">Lingard ch\u1ec9 ra l\u00fd do \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/colombia-co-noi-gian-trong-doi-tuyen-anh-421-190124.html\">Colombia c\u00f3 &ldquo;n\u1ed9i gi\u00e1n&rdquo; trong \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/doi-tuyen-anh-san-sang-pha-dop-luan-luu-11m-421-190119.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ph\u00e1 d\u1edbp lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/rooney-doi-tuyen-anh-se-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-469-190108.html\">Rooney: \u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N.D (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"818","checkdouble":"190181"},{"date":"16:43 02/07","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m v\u00f2ng 17 V-League: H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng, HAGL chia \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/du-am-vong-17-vleague-ha-noi-tien-sat-ngoi-vuong-hagl-chia-diem-dang-tiec.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, HAGL ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u1edf v\u00f2ng 17 V-League.</h2><h2>1. H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u0103ng b\u0103ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf khi ph\u1ea3i di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n C\u1ea9m Ph\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh tuy nhi\u00ean H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng sau 17 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1edbm sau pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh Vinicius \u1edf ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 8 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng b\u1eb1ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm t\u00e1i l\u1eadp th\u1ebf c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng sau c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Ph\u1ea1m Th\u00e0nh L\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf ph\u00fat 31. 5 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 V\u0103n Ki\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 t\u1edbi h\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ngay t\u1ea1i C\u1ea9m Ph\u1ea3, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc \u1edf ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi 44 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp sau l\u00e0 Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a BVN \u0111\u1ebfn 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m, m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch qu\u00e1 an to\u00e0n cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m v\u00f2ng 17 V-League H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng, HAGL chia \u0111i\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m v\u00f2ng 17 V-League H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng, HAGL chia \u0111i\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/a00-8311-1530455756.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc 5 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. HAGL b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 17 V-League, CLB HAGL c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang gi\u1eef ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u00e0 CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t Qu\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Claudecir kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn kh\u00e1 l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean b\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, khi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng, &lsquo;G\u1ed7&rsquo; \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng v\u00e0i ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u khi\u1ebfn HAGL \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi Tam K\u1ef3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00f2a tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, CLB HAGL&nbsp;v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i l\u1ea1i m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Qu\u1ea3ng Nam tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Pleiku \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 5 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng v\u1edbi 24 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. SLNA l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 6<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 5 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, CLB SLNA kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ed1p 3 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i V-League 2018. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn sau v\u00f2ng 17 V-League, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 23 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u00fang 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec m\u1ea1ch tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, SLNA ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n tr\u00ean BXH tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u1ebft th\u00fac. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">SLNA thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong th\u1eddi gian qua c\u0169ng nh\u1edd v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c. Sau hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i L\u1ea1ch Tray b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e2ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 3-0&nbsp;\u1edf ph\u00fat 69 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i chung cu\u1ed9c 3-2 trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i L\u1ea1ch Tray.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 ghi b\u00e0n n\u00e0y, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hai Phong vs SLNA\" title=\"H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs SLNA\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/nhan-dinh-hai-phong-vs-slna-17h00-ngay-17-vleague-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>SLNA \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng t\u1ea1i L\u1ea1ch Tray</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>4. S\u00e0i G\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00eam c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 s\u00edt sao 1-0 nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Thanh H\u00f3a L\u00ea Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 90 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap S\u00e0i G\u00f2n t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u00ean BXH m\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, n\u00f3 c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u00eam quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a CLB tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng an to\u00e0n. L\u00fac n\u00e0y S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 h\u01a1n TP.HCM 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu duy tr\u00ec m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf l\u1ea1i V-League m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2019.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/1/Highlight-Quang-Ninh-vs-Ha-Noi.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH sau vong 17 V-League 2018\" title=\"BXH sau v\u00f2ng 17 V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/BXH-sau-vong-17-V-League-2018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BXH sau v\u00f2ng 17 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/diem-nhan-quang-nam-22-hagl-cu-dup-cua-van-toan-168-190109.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/van-toan-ghi-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/diem-nhan-quang-nam-22-hagl-cu-dup-cua-van-toan-168-190109.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 2-2 HAGL: C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u1edf v\u00f2ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam-168-190172.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam-168-190172.html\">HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u00f9 h\u1ecd m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/de-thua-tuong-moi-cua-sai-gon-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi-168-190140.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/de-thua-tuong-moi-cua-sai-gon-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/de-thua-tuong-moi-cua-sai-gon-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi-168-190140.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 thua t\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, HLV Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"817","checkdouble":"190182"}]}